OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy today with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain and drizzle where the cloud
OL,7,Fthickens. Low cloud will bring some
OL,8,Fearly hill fog, but this should lift
OL,9,Finto the afternoon. Some brighter
OL,10,Fspells are possible in Anglesey
OL,11,Fthrough the day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLow cloud will continue to
OL,14,Fbring showery outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fovernight, and some fog over the hills
OL,16,Ftoo. Staying frost free under the
OL,17,Fblanket of cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
