OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,6,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain. Skies
OL,7,Fwill brighten a little later on with
OL,8,Fsome hazy spells of sunshine.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FPatchy
OL,11,Fcloud and sunny spells on Tuesday, and
OL,12,Fthe odd shower. Turning increasingly
OL,13,Fwindy thereafter with spells of rain
OL,14,Fand scattered showers, and some
OL,15,Fbrighter interludes too. Near normal
OL,16,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
